{
  "texts": [
    "Reward Hacking Prevention.",
    "During the early stage of experiments, we observed some reward-hacking issues during training.",
    "For instance, the model will generate some artifacts like \"all instructions are followed\" or \"this is a perfect response that meets all requirements!\"",
    "in responses to mislead the rubric verifier to give a spurious high reward.",
    "While finetuning a rubric verifier can help to mitigate this issue (Section 4.3), we further include two additional criteria into each data point as a reward shaping technique:"
  ]
}